<table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0"><tr><td class="t_f" id="postmessage_77867609">
徐科任中国红十字会党组书记 被提名常务副会长人选<br />

<ignore_js_op>

<img id="aimg_5880622" aid="5880622" src="static/image/common/none.gif" zoomfile="http://f3.rednet.cn/data/attachment/forum/201409/02/231932ad5cwu5jqdcic14j.jpg" file="http://f3.rednet.cn/data/attachment/forum/201409/02/231932ad5cwu5jqdcic14j.jpg" class="zoom" onclick="zoom(this, this.src, 0, 0, 1)" width="600" id="aimg_5880622" inpost="1" onmouseover="showMenu({'ctrlid':this.id,'pos':'12'})" />

